&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with frontend frameworks &amp;amp; tooling (React, Slack Block Kit, dashboard components) to build user-facing interfaces for AI tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with vector databases or retrieval pipelines (Pinecone, Weaviate, ChromaDB, pgvector, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
